                "text": "I find screens vs not screens to be a useful distinction here. I think Dynamicland is trying to show us the way away from screens. Meanwhile for the large amount of work that will continue to be done on screens, things could be a lot better (and a lot of the work itself could probably be eliminated — bullshit jobs).\n"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
